cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically addressing the problem of 3D reconstruction and material recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of robots in nuclear decommissioning indicates the category cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The paper also involves segmentation, which suggests the category cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the use of end-to-end learning suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
